#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Function Editor lists all the functions that you have plotted. If "
#| "<guilabel>y = x^2</guilabel> isn't already selected, select it. Here you "
#| "have access to a lot of options. Let us rename the function and move the "
